{"tid":457244,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜成立左六,七年既「初創企業」贏得創業比賽金獎!!","createTime":"2017-11-03T16:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T09:19:27.000Z","uid":39941,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"be48708b67a0674ccd6b0d2e2ba5b672eb6c1ba2","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"頭先放左起吹水台,但太快比人洗走, 依件事都關創意事,所以轉post起到<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有留意ACG+Capital果個比賽? 今日出結果, 金獎係Touchdown: Armor League, 個人覺得個畫面係幾靚, 之前佢kickstart果時都有留意, 但係諗諗下又唔對路, 去簡介會既時候明明聽過大會d人講過參加者唔可以持有營運緊既公司, 之後聽其他參賽者講話大會講明唔可以有同業務公司, 作為初創公司比賽, 佢地又好似唔係符合資格, 所以我就去google搵多d資料<br />\n<br />\n起google到搵到佢間公司叫ares games, 上佢官網好似已經死左, 但我再搵清d, (起google cache到查, 結果係:<br />\n<br />\nThis is Google's cache of <a href=\"https://www.aresgames.com.hk/.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aresgames.com.hk%2F.&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7dab1f0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aresgames.com.hk/.</a> It is a snapshot of the page as it appeared on 23 Oct 2017 23:59:24 GMT. <br />\n<br />\n姐係佢10月23號先死 ) ,但比我搵到<a href=\"https://www.aresgames.com.hk/products \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aresgames.com.hk%2Fproducts%20&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=4db6550f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aresgames.com.hk/products </a>依個網, 入面有佢隻Touchdown: Armor League, 仲有另一隻叫hell warders既game<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/000022_0dc4aac6a75d0bb91785859344cfed5f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F000022_0dc4aac6a75d0bb91785859344cfed5f.PNG&h=215cfe0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHerll warders 係最近先上steam既game<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/000041_0173c51c2dedc05bb81bfb49ca2ee6db.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F000041_0173c51c2dedc05bb81bfb49ca2ee6db.PNG&h=55220cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDeveloper 係Anti gravity games studio, 但起隻game個官網到又寫佢係ares games<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/000051_2f3d7c17c949e158cf2fc9063af619b7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F000051_2f3d7c17c949e158cf2fc9063af619b7.PNG&h=a059a3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就上公司注冊處個網到查下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/000108_92c62c3fdc2d0cd32b7a47b25941e398.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F000108_92c62c3fdc2d0cd32b7a47b25941e398.PNG&h=c8ef32cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/000117_a9f6262884ffa5617d8922a24e28151f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F000117_a9f6262884ffa5617d8922a24e28151f.PNG&h=7dbf1f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哇屌, 2間公司同一日轉祕書同董事, 仲要係公布結果2日前先轉,明顯係想「回避」有同業務公司依樣野, 但唔係一開始參加就已經要符合最基本既條件?<br />\n<br />\n咁都叫做無同業務公司?<br />\n咁姐係我搵間公司整定隻game,下年如果仲有依個比賽就將成隻game過比我參加咪得? 或是本身如果我有間公司,可以整定多隻game, 下年再開間新公司, 去拎40萬, 咁咪fat fat?<br />\n<br />\n大會係無打算理定係無去查,咁都可以符合要求? 個比賽唔係講到係想支持扶助初創企業發展咩, 如果佢本身有一間營運過6-7年既公司, 又有一隻賣緊既產品, 咁都叫「初創企業」?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FZx9dM219Dw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFZx9dM219Dw&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3752f7f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FZx9dM219Dw</a><br />\n0:43果到佢間野十尻幾條友, 仲要個個雙mon, 咁都當佢係新公司未營運? 唔洗諗住刪左條片無人知,已經backup左<br />\n<br />\n起到恭喜另外9組年青人可以實現理想, 不過好似有幾間唔多關acg事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b970af4f983f15714a9afca521aac5d44e300400","tid":457244,"uid":19638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfd90a1658d1a628b1fdc048dc922cb5f2508ee","tid":457244,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T18:37:29.000Z","msg":"我諗放時事台先多人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f31dc680a45b3ce24b7776052edefb3ad89673","tid":457244,"uid":103497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T19:28:02.000Z","msg":"難得見到<br />\n幫手推下"},{"pid":"3550b507a844d59c0eb13922335701439965bf0a","tid":457244,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:29:24.000Z","msg":"私相授受"},{"pid":"916d49345c951f2b5d9e4c82fc47cb699351ef7b","tid":457244,"uid":73454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:44:38.000Z","msg":"所以無論比幾多錢政府佢搞創新科技，我地d錢都使左去去左某班人身上"},{"pid":"8894ba819bc4f03392be01be325cac3e3b0158ce","tid":457244,"uid":76809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:49:57.000Z","msg":"推 多謝大家支持左手交右手"},{"pid":"4ed676f771b27ff1cd07840c5861185ab75c21a0","tid":457244,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T20:53:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f4dfd3007cb55a793aca430f1f32a69c3827cf5","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"765b6a6f83e109217805e9b29647950f847fd555","tid":457244,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"去大會投訴，搵蘋果呢啲傳媒爆料"},{"pid":"4b97ec48f4d4bdad9053a1f7825e388ffdf9bbf0","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/224134_02e7797a625cc5b7ef639d4e53a8742d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F224134_02e7797a625cc5b7ef639d4e53a8742d.jpeg&h=f607fd68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哇，講到自己好撚辛苦咁，又辭職參賽，辭職自己另一間遊戲公司既董事呀？<br />\n我就買佢果間anti gravity gams既法團成立表格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/224147_5ea3ad1fceffec4e3b32acf89ec1be62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F224147_5ea3ad1fceffec4e3b32acf89ec1be62.jpg&h=94942c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇屌，原來董事叫劉嘉明，咁似其中一個參加者個名既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好以為11月1號走去辭職就搵你唔到呀<br />\n<br />\n好偉大! 好熱血!!!!!<br />\n(幫你刪左身份證no. ,唔洗多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"f449c8339361cb9762bca866bf0ca2814b84c894","tid":457244,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212bf7ffb7f932921026d0aea4e0ab9b65049c0d","tid":457244,"uid":6684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275a0b04c1acb6de169fb5d7f62aa67c2cd409a6","tid":457244,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"af55808b03e623558d3af7cf6f9cc94a54d9f340","tid":457244,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1931735144d6a5dec6ba498171b86c78e0ddfe20","tid":457244,"uid":81156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class