9Dw</a><br />\n*留意返個時game producer and director 叫 Wei Gu (0:40) 話已經整左五年大陸game想轉攻western market<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7月28</span>    ACG初創比賽簡介會<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7月31</span>    開左新公司 AntiGravity Games Ltd.<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">8月</span>        新公司AntiGravity Games Ltd. 用同一隻game申請比賽<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">10月25</span>  係kickstarter將隻game嘅公司改做AntiGravity Games Ltd. 再心虛close左個page <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/dmca/touchdown-armor-league-submitted-by-antigravity-games-ltd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fdmca%2Ftouchdown-armor-league-submitted-by-antigravity-games-ltd&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e58f25b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/dmca/touchdown-armor-league-submitted-by-antigravity-games-ltd</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">11月1</span>     新舊公司一齊轉董事, 舊公司摺埋<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">11月3</span>     原director唔知係邊, 另外三個人拎獎 yeah<br />\n<br />\n再睇埋報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/11/04/YO1711040014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2FYO1711040014.htm&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=edc89e27\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/11/04/YO1711040014.htm</a><br />\n&quot;現年30歲的劉嘉明退出原本有份開設的遊戲開發公司&quot;<br />\n&quot;今年暑假時得知有今次比賽才決定退出公司，與同事黃擎峯一同利用已擱置的概念參賽&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁計係咪7月中尾得知比賽就辭職, 31號就開左新公司, 11月1正式上任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗諗住同主辦講喇, 分分鐘主辦係完全知情加ok, 臨拎獎仲提佢地好快快趣搞埋啲手續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充</blockquote><br />\n轉貼返另一個post另一巴打既懶人包<br />\n未必全部真, 例如舊公司未摺<br />\n<br />\n補充翻一點, 果間野未必係用ares games或者antigravity games 名義參賽, 不過無論如何應該都不合資格"},{"pid":"a334a72292846c664898a28ea8f25ede98b2b88a","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"