都抄人咁 darksoul 逆轉裁判 仲要隻隻完成度都好撚高 個比賽真係分豬肉咁分"},{"pid":"857a315447fa5a596de2b15e8c02369f417377f6","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WKWwZdn-pI0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWKWwZdn-pI0&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=62bd811f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WKWwZdn-pI0</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e5e4233aef23ab696af5a76a4bbad4f09c55cc","tid":457244,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd79b5f92cdbf096b8e0b2ab038e6a8c13f51aa","tid":457244,"uid":138644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e546043a14a277d594479634b9d70847cfa934dd","tid":457244,"uid":12176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"其實咁撚樣走法律罅都幾撚輕鬆...資源靠大公司，開間新公司扮startup 呃funding.個濕鳩政府又真係fund 俾呢啲咁嘅公司，証明個政府都係求鳩其做下野。"},{"pid":"ed7a2ecc57dc761a29456a5ead74d3a26901b249","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/acgcapital-%E5%8B%95%E6%BC%AB%E7%8E%A9%E5%89%B5%E4%B9%8B%E9%83%BD/%E6%9C%AC%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E5%92%8C%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96/169198640329697/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2Facgcapital-%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%2583%25BD%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E5%2592%258C%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%2F169198640329697%2F&d=L6KG9P2XCiqNAb3fW3O%2BaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c1b971c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/acgcapital-%E5%8B%95%E6%BC%AB%E7%8E%A9%E5%89%B5%E4%B9%8B%E9%83%BD/%E6%9C%AC%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E5%92%8C%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96/169198640329697/</a><br />\n大會回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cf2d71dae8386930cb6f2ba70f0897c6fbc07d","tid":457244,"uid":152692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/139626/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/139626/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地幾個月之前仲要係連登開過post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  證明最少當時已經出左隻game。<br />\n<br />\n我同幾個朋友都參加左個比賽，有參加既人應該感受到佢地既規則係陰人，跟足佢地規則去做既話係輸硬。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都參加左，老實講D規則根本唔清唔楚，所以根本唔知佢準則係乜嘢。我係apply game，但班評審根本唔係玩開game嘅人，做商又唔係，真係9唔撘8。<br />\n<br />\n其實本身都預左入面一定係比圍內自己友贏，只係希望搏到其餘個2-3個位。佢開talk係deadline兩個禮拜之前。。。正常人係只有兩個禮拜準備。宜家佢拎堆接近完成品出嚟，點同佢玩。"},{"pid":"844b8d8ec056e08e7ec57eb84eb3aabfef967477","tid":457244,"uid":39941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"整合左集合POST, 請主力推依個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/459599/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/459599/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7faa666d22a64c88622f753d062efa4b9b221e35","tid":457244,"uid":80719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"a683e0a56b892cbaa420861cb01a82b33c5cc80b","tid":457244,"uid":